headline: NetApp Stock Rides Rising AI Tide; Shares Popped 70% In The Last 5 Months
summary: NetApp is gaining traction amid the artificial intelligence tech boom.  Shares of San Jose, Calif.-based NetApp are on track for a sixth straight week of higher closes.  NetApp makes integrated network storage and data management equipment for corporations and government agencies.

headline: NetApp Modernizes Object Storage with Enhanced Speed, Scalability and Security
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., September 09, 2025--NetApp® (NASDAQ: NTAP), the intelligent data infrastructure company, today announced NetApp StorageGRID® 12.0, a scalable, software-defined object storage solution designed for unstructured data. This latest version of StorageGRID will introduce new capabilities designed to enhance AI initiatives, improve data security, and modernize organizations’ data infrastructure.
